A '''ruby''' is a red [[Gems|gem]] used in [[Crafting]] and [[Fletching]]. Rubies can be cut from [[uncut ruby|uncut rubies]] with level 34 Crafting by using a [[chisel]], granting 85 experience. When used with a [[furnace]] and [[jewellery]] [[mould]], they can be used to make ruby jewellery.

A one-time reward of two cut rubies can be obtained by using a chisel and [[hammer]] on [[Thammaron]]'s throne during [[The Golem]] quest. Four cut rubies are also obtained as a reward for completing [[Olaf's Quest]].

